    m_Alignment: 0
    m_AlignByGeometry: 0
    m_RichText: 1
    m_HorizontalOverflow: 0
    m_VerticalOverflow: 0
    m_LineSpacing: 1
  m_Text: "How To Play:\n\nCharge the Plunger to launch the ball, \nscore points
    by having your ball hit\nthe bumpers, and use the flippers \nto prolong how long
    your ball remains\non the table.\n\nYou have 3 balls\n\nControls:\n\n- Hold SPACE
    to charge plunger\n- A & D to activate Flippers\n\n- Press R to reset ball\n-
    Pressing 1 gives you a ball\n- Pressing 2 removes a ball\n-"
